   Javier Valtuena, Francisco; Lopez, Josefa; Ortega-Olivencia, Ana; Rodriguez-Riano, Tomas, Univ Extremadura, Fac Sci, Area Bot, Badajoz, Spain.
   Gonzalez, Miguel, Univ Extremadura, Fac Sci, Area Stat \& Operat Res, Badajoz, Spain.},
