   Langgut, Dafna, Tel Aviv Univ, Dept Archaeol \& Ancient Near Eastern Cultures, Steinhardt Museum Nat Hist, Tel Aviv, Israel.
   Langgut, Dafna, Tel Aviv Univ, Steinhardt Museum Nat Hist, Tel Aviv, Israel.
   Vereecken, Nicolas J., Univ Libre Bruxelles ULB, Agroecol Lab, Brussels, Belgium.},
